Jessa Monroe Portfolio - Technical Style GuideThis document outlines the visual design system, color palette, and coding conventions for the jessamonroe.com static website.1. Color PaletteThe site uses a custom earthy palette defined in the <style> block of the HTML.Color NameHex CodeCSS ClassUsageSage Green#4A5D4E.bg-sage / .text-sagePrimary action color, headings, active states.Deep Blue#2C3E50.bg-deep-blueFooter background, high-contrast sections.Olive#A3B18A.bg-olive / .text-oliveAccents, icons, secondary highlights.Sand#F4F1EA.bg-sandPage background, alternating sections.Taupe#D7C9B1.border-taupeBorders, dividers.Slate Blue#4E6B7B(Custom CSS)Body text hyperlinks.Slate Hover#3D5A6C(Custom CSS)Body text hyperlink hover state.Button Specifics:Primary Button Hover: #5A6F5F (A slightly lighter/muted Sage for contrast).2. TypographyFont Family: Inter (via Google Fonts).Weights Used:300 (Light)400 (Regular)500 (Medium)600 (Semi-bold)3. UI ComponentsButtonsButtons use a pill-shape radius (rounded-full) with generous padding.Primary (Solid):<a class="px-10 py-4 rounded-full bg-sage text-white font-medium hover:bg-[#5A6F5F] transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
Secondary (Outline):<a class="px-10 py-4 rounded-full border border-taupe/50 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm text-sage font-medium hover:bg-white transition-all">
CardsCards are designed with soft borders and large border radii to feel organic and non-rigid.Standard Card: rounded-3xl, border-taupe/20, bg-white or bg-sand.Glassmorphism Card: Used in the "Symptoms" section.Classes: bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm border-olive/20.HyperlinksNavigation: No underline, inherits text color, changes to Olive on hover.Body Content: Slate Blue (#4E6B7B), underlined with an offset (text-underline-offset: 4px).4. Coding ConventionsStrict Rules for MaintainabilityNo Semicolons:JavaScript must rely on Automatic Semicolon Insertion (ASI).Do not use semicolons in text copy or scripts.Text Formatting:No Em-dashes (—): Use standard punctuation.Sentence Structure: Avoid "It's not X. It's Y." phrasing. Use descriptive transitions instead.Tailwind Usage:Use utility classes for layout (flex, grid, padding).Use the defined custom classes (.text-sage) for colors to ensure brand consistency across the single file.Icons:Library: Lucide Icons.Implementation: <i data-lucide="icon-name"></i>.Initialization: lucide.createIcons() script at the bottom of the body.5. SEO & Meta Data ConfigurationEnsure these tags remain accurate if content changes:Title: Jessa Monroe | Somatic Counseling for Anxiety & Feeling Stuck in Peabody, MACanonical: https://jessamonroe.comLocal SEO: Address data for Serenity Now Counseling LLC (2 Bourbon Street, Peabody & 6 Eastman Pl, Melrose) is hardcoded in the JSON-LD script in the <head>.6. Directory StructureThis project is a single-page static site./ (root)
├── index.html       # Main entry point (Production code)
├── style-guide.md   # This documentation
├── image-0.jpg      # Fallback local image (if remote fails)
└── README.md        # General repo info
